Earl J. Hesterberg 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at GROUP 1 AUTOMOTIVE INC, Earl J. Hesterberg  made $4,337,265 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,100,000 was received as a salary, $1,210,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,813,700 was awarded as stock and $213,565 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


